text: Marjory Saunders was a Canadian archer from Great Britain. She was born on 10 March 1913 in Sussex and died on 26 November 2010 in Maple Ridge, British Columbia. Saunders competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics.Marjory SaundersMarjorie SAUNDERS == References == Category:1913 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Canadian archers Category:Olympians for Canada
